topic.title: Medication Free Text Sig - conformance rules

section.p:
The template is available to explicitly identify the free text Sig within each medication.
An example free text sig: Thyroxin 150 ug, take one tab by mouth every morning

ol.li:
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] templateId ( CONF:1198-32753, CONF:1198-32772 ) such that it
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @root="2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.22.4.147"

SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @moodCode, which SHALL be selected from ValueSet MoodCodeEvnInt 2.16.840.1.113883.11.20.9.18 STATIC 2011-04-03 (CONF:1198-32771)
Note: moodCode must match the parent substanceAdministration EVN or INT
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] code (CONF:1198-32775)/@code="76662-6" Instructions Medication (CodeSystem: 2.16.840.1.113883.6.1 LOINC) (CONF:1198-32780, CONF:1198-32781)

SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] consumable such that it (CONF:1198-32776)
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] manufacturedProduct such that it (CONF:1198-32777)
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] manufacturedLabeledDrug such that it (CONF:1198-32778)
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @nullFlavor="NA" (CONF:1198-32779)
reference/@value SHALL begin with a '#' and SHALL point to its corresponding narrative (using the approach defined in CDA Release 2, section 4.3.5.1) (CONF:1198-32774)

SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @moodCode, which SHALL be selected from ValueSet MoodCodeEvnInt 2.16.840.1.113883.11.20.9.18 STATIC 2011-04-03 (CONF:1198-32771)
Note: moodCode must match the parent substanceAdministration EVN or INT
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] code (CONF:1198-32775)/@code="76662-6" Instructions Medication (CodeSystem: 2.16.840.1.113883.6.1 LOINC) (CONF:1198-32780, CONF:1198-32781)

SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] consumable such that it (CONF:1198-32776)
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] manufacturedProduct such that it (CONF:1198-32777)
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] manufacturedLabeledDrug such that it (CONF:1198-32778)
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @nullFlavor="NA" (CONF:1198-32779)
reference/@value SHALL begin with a '#' and SHALL point to its corresponding narrative (using the approach defined in CDA Release 2, section 4.3.5.1) (CONF:1198-32774)
